sequenceDiagram
    participant Dispatch as 调度器
    participant Prompts as auto-prompts.ts
    participant Budget as context-budget.ts
    participant Files as .gsd/ 磁盘文件
    participant Prefs as preferences.ts

    Dispatch->>Prompts: buildExecuteTaskPrompt(ctx)
    Prompts->>Prefs: loadEffectiveGSDPreferences()
    Prefs-->>Prompts: {inline_level: "full", context_window: 200000}
    Prompts->>Budget: computeBudgets(windowTokens)
    Budget-->>Prompts: {preambleChars: 30000, inlineContextChars: 60000}
    Prompts->>Files: loadFile(MILESTONE.md)
    Files-->>Prompts: milestone 内容
    Prompts->>Files: loadFile(SLICE.md)
    Files-->>Prompts: slice 内容
    Prompts->>Prompts: capPreamble(preamble, 30000)
    Note over Prompts: 按章节边界智能截断，不硬截字符
    Prompts-->>Dispatch: 裁剪后的完整 Prompt